summary:
Geologist from the University of Kansas. I have had 2 years of research experience, in geochronology and cosmogenic dating, and a short span in the industry (geotechnical investigation, soil sampling, ground analysis). I have also spent time at the Oregon Museum of Science and Industry, teaching geology to students at the primary and middle school levels. 
Having recently moved to the Netherlands, I am looking for opportunities in geotechnical investigation and analysis in the Eindhoven area.
